maneuvers.narrative: Start out going southeast on E 1st St toward S Los Angeles St.
Turn left onto N Los Angeles St.
Merge onto US-101 S.
Merge onto I-10 E via EXIT 1D on the left toward San Bernardino/I-10 E.
Merge onto I-605 N via EXIT 31B.
Merge onto I-210 E toward San Bernardino/Foothill Fwy.
I-210 E becomes CA-210 E.
Merge onto I-15 N via EXIT 64A toward Barstow (Passing through Nevada and Arizona, then crossing into Utah).
Merge onto I-70 E via EXIT 132 toward Denver/Richfield (Crossing into Colorado).
Keep left to take I-76 E via EXIT 269B toward Ft Morgan (Crossing into Nebraska).
I-76 E becomes I-80 E (Crossing into Iowa).
Merge onto I-280 E via EXIT 290 toward Rock Island/Moline/US-61 S (Crossing into Illinois).
I-280 E becomes I-80 E (Portions toll) (Crossing into Indiana).
Merge onto I-80 E via EXIT 16 toward Ohio (Portions toll) (Crossing into Ohio).
Merge onto I-80 E via EXIT 218 toward Youngstown (Passing through Pennsylvania, then crossing into New Jersey).
Stay straight to go onto I-80 (EXPRESS) E.
Merge onto I-280 E via EXIT 47A on the left toward The Oranges/Newark.
Take EXIT 17A toward Jersey City/County Hwy-508 E.
Merge onto Newark Turnpike.
Keep right at the fork to go on NJ-7.
Merge onto NJ-139 E via the ramp on the left toward Holland Tunnel/Hoboken (Portions toll) (Crossing into New York).
NJ-139 E becomes Holland Tunnel/I-78 E (Portions toll).
Turn slight left (Portions toll).
Turn slight left onto Beach St (Portions toll).
Keep right at the fork to continue on Beach St.
Beach St becomes Walker St.
Turn right onto Broadway.
Welcome to NEW YORK, NY.
